{"id":4862,"date":"2026-02-26T19:40:32","date_gmt":"2026-02-26T19:40:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/loungenie.com\/staging\/?page_id=4862"},"modified":"2026-03-24T12:57:06","modified_gmt":"2026-03-24T12:57:06","slug":"hospitality-innovation","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/loungenie.com\/staging\/hospitality-innovation\/","title":{"rendered":"About LounGenie | Hospitality Technology for Premium Seating"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover is-dark lg9-page-hero\" style=\"padding-top:84px;padding-right:24px;padding-bottom:84px;padding-left:24px;min-height:500px;aspect-ratio:unset;\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-black-background-color has-background-dim-52 has-background-dim\"><\/span><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background\" alt=\"Hospitality Innovation\" src=\"https:\/\/loungenie.com\/staging\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/lg-about-westin-hilton-head-scaled.jpg\" style=\"object-position:50% 36%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"50% 36%\"\/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-a31aa551 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size:clamp(31.609px, 1.976rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 2.541), 56px);line-height:1.02\">Hospitality Innovation<\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-size:clamp(14px, 0.875rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.625), 20px);line-height:1.8\">Built in Canada by PoolSafe to help operators improve guest experience, service speed, and poolside revenue.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\"><div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/loungenie.com\/staging\/contact-loungenie\/\">Request a Demo<\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-16a996fa wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:72px;padding-right:24px;padding-bottom:72px;padding-left:24px\"><p>Why It Works<\/p>\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A practical operating tool, not just another cabana accessory.<\/h2>\n\n<p>LounGenie is purpose-built for hospitality operations. It combines service enablement and guest convenience at the seat, where it matters most.<\/p>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\"><div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">ORDER<\/h3><p>QR ordering sends requests to a dedicated PoolSafe printer for staff execution.<\/p><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">STASH<\/h3><p>Waterproof safe with waterproof keypad for secure guest storage.<\/p><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">CHARGE + CHILL<\/h3><p>Solar USB charging and a removable ice bucket for all-day comfort.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tier structure for every property type<\/h2>\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><strong>Classic:<\/strong> STASH + CHARGE + CHILL<\/li><li><strong>Service+:<\/strong> Classic + service-call button alerting staff touchscreen monitor<\/li><li><strong>2.0:<\/strong> Service+ + QR ordering (call button remains active)<\/li><\/ul>\n\n<p>PoolSafe provides installation, maintenance, and service through a zero-upfront, revenue-share model.<\/p>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\"><div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/loungenie.com\/staging\/poolside-amenity-unit\/\">Explore Product Features<\/a><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-outline is-style-outline--1\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/loungenie.com\/staging\/cabana-installation-photos\/\">View Installation Photos<\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Learn how LounGenie was built for premium hospitality environments with operator practicality, commercial-grade design, and guest-focused technology.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":8380,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"page-wide","meta":{"content-type":"","footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-4862","page","type-page","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/loungenie.com\/staging\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/4862","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/loungenie.com\/staging\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/loungenie.com\/staging\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/loungenie.com\/staging\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/loungenie.com\/staging\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4862"}],"version-history":[{"count":269,"href":"https:\/\/loungenie.com\/staging\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/4862\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":9230,"href":"https:\/\/loungenie.com\/staging\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/4862\/revisions\/9230"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/loungenie.com\/staging\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/8380"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/loungenie.com\/staging\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4862"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}